Definition: a smart bomb that seeks the laser light reflected off of the target and uses it to correct its descent
Example: laser-guided bombs cannot be used in cloudy weather
Synonyms: LGB, smart_bomb, a, smart, bomb, that, seeks, the, laser, light, reflected, off, of, target, and, uses, it, to, correct, its, descent, laser-guided, bombs, cannot, be, used, in, cloudy, weather
Category: noun.artifact
